tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE influencer_partnerships (
	id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
	influencer_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
	partner_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
	collaboration_type VARCHAR(50),
	collaboration_start_date DATE,
	collaboration_end_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE influencer_partner (
    partner_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    influencer_id INT,
    partnership_start_date DATE,
    partnership_end_date DATE,
    collaboration_description TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE collaboration_details (
    collaboration_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    partner_id INT,
    influencer_id INT,
    collaboration_date DATE,
    collaboration_type VARCHAR(255),
    audience_reach INT
);

CREATE TABLE Partnerships (
    partnership_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    influencer_id INT,
    partner_id INT,
    partnership_type VARCHAR(50),
    partnership_date DATE,
    PRIMARY KEY(partnership_id),
    FOREIGN KEY(influencer_id) REFERENCES Influencers(influencer_id),
    FOREIGN KEY(partner_id) REFERENCES Partners(partner_id)
);

CREATE TABLE Collaborations (
    collaboration_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    partnership_id INT,
    collaboration_details TEXT,
    collaboration_date DATE,
    FOREIGN KEY(partnership_id) REFERENCES Partnerships(partnership_id)
);

CREATE TABLE Collaborations (
    collaboration_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    influencer_id INT,
    brand_id INT,
    collaboration_date DATE,
    campaign_name VARCHAR(100)
);

CREATE TABLE Metrics (
    metric_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    collaboration_id INT,
    engagement_rate DECIMAL,
    reach INT,
    impressions INT
);
CREATE TABLE influencers ( influencer_id INT PRIMARY KEY, influencer_name VARCHAR(50), follower_count INT, category VARCHAR(50) );
CREATE TABLE brands ( brand_id INT PRIMARY KEY, brand_name VARCHAR(50), industry VARCHAR(50) );
CREATE TABLE partnerships ( partnership_id INT PRIMARY KEY, influencer_id INT, brand_id INT, start_date DATE, end_date DATE, payment_amount DECIMAL(10, 2), collaboration_description TEXT );
CREATE TABLE collaboration_types ( collaboration_type_id INT PRIMARY KEY, collaboration_type_name VARCHAR(50) );
CREATE TABLE collaboration_history ( collaboration_id INT PRIMARY KEY, partnership_id INT, collaboration_type_id INT, collaboration_date DATE, engagement_rate DECIMAL(5, 2) );
